  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div class=\"qti-layout-row\"> <div class=\"qti-layout-col12\"> <div class=\"prompt\"> <p class=\"dap_body\">​In the&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"x y\"><math alttext=\"x y\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>-plane, the terminal ray of an angle in standard position intersects the unit circle at point&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>. Which of the following is true about the cosine of the angle, as the angle measure increases from&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"0\"><math alttext=\"0\"><semantics><mn>0</mn><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"pi\"><math alttext=\"pi\"><semantics><mi>π</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;?</p> </div> </div> </div>\n",
    "answer": "B-61049",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​The cosine of the angle decreases then increases, because the horizontal displacement of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;from the&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\"><semantics><mi>y</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>-axis decreases, then increases over the interval.</p>",
        "value": "A-61048"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​The cosine of the angle decreases, because the horizontal displacement of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;from the&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\"><semantics><mi>y</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>-axis decreases over the entire interval.</p>",
        "value": "B-61049"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​The cosine of the angle increases, then decreases, because the vertical displacement of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;from the&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>-axis increases, then decreases over the interval.</p>",
        "value": "C-61050"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"dap_body\">​​​The cosine of the angle decreases, because the vertical displacement of&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\"><semantics><mi>P</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>&nbsp;from the&nbsp;<span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\"><semantics><mi>x</mi><annotation encoding=\"application/vnd.wiris.mtweb-params+json\">{\"digitSeparatorsAsMN\":\"auto\"}</annotation></semantics></math></span>-axis decreases over the entire interval.</p>",
